uniol.apt.analysis.synthesize

Class SynthesizePN.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • uniol.apt.analysis.synthesize.SynthesizePN.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    SynthesizePN

    public static class SynthesizePN.Builder
extends java.lang.Object
    Builder class for creating instances of SynthesizePN. You create an instance of this class via createForIsomorphicBehaviour or createForLanguageEquivalence, give it all the state that you want and then use one of the build() method to create a SynthesizePN instance.

      • setQuickFail

        public SynthesizePN.Builder setQuickFail(boolean qf)
        Set the quick fail mode for the SynthesizePN instance. Use quick fail mode if only the result from SynthesizePN.wasSuccessfullySeparated() is interesting for you. In this case, SynthesizePN will stop after the first failure instead of going through all separation problems and trying to solve them. The quick fail mode default to false.
        Parameters:
        qf - the new value for the quick fail mode.
        Returns:
        this
